modName: Unique Region Names - Patched for USLEEP
summary: Carries over changes made to exteriors by the Unofficial Skyrim Legendary Edition Patch to Unique Region Names.
descriptionHtml:
Carries over changes made to exteriors by the Unofficial Skyrim Legendary Edition Patch to Unique Region Names.

Place it low in your load order so this mod's name changes don't get overwritten.

Post a bug report if any other exterior cells are missing name changes, or if a bugfix needs to be forwarded.
author: Thingy Person
